title: Lost Planet (Eclipse)
description:
The ECUP drives to the Pine Barrens to dispose of a dead hooker, with 'Lost Planet'!

Lost Planet is a six-issue mini written and illustrated by Bo Hampton and published by Eclipse in 1987-88. Set in 1938, it's the story of Tyler Flynn, treasure hunter and soldier of fortune, who is transported to a world of monsters and magic.


This torrent has all six issues, PLUS a DCP Archive Edition that collects the whole story. Best wishes to the creators and scanners! Download, upload!
